"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實香港手球同合球隊，一直係亞洲都好似有唔錯ga成績，只係少人注視。</blockquote><br />\n小眾運動冇人睇有乜出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我記得之前合球(香港代表隊)好似為左出國比賽，要跑圈籌錢</blockquote><br />\n政府淨係識泵水啲精英運動<br />\n啲非精英運動冇資源點發展做精英運動啫<br />\n呢啲所謂非精英運動嘅運動員甚至要自費租場訓練 出國比賽 扼殺咗好多有潛力嘅人嘅機會"},{"pid":"61037705974f5ab76a829d82326a78f1cad45d89","tid":374722,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港手球同合球隊，一直係亞洲都好似有唔錯ga成績，只係少人注視。</blockquote><br />\n但真係柒過籃波好多"},{"pid":"1965e19df23a00406438b58a605335138ec7720e","tid":374722,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將會有大量低能兒沖出黎柒</blockquote><br />\n何解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca6ffa51fa80b7cfc0ee9129c2be7fa3e7037c9","tid":374722,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實香港手球同合球隊，一直係亞洲都好似有唔錯ga成績，只係少人注視。</blockquote><br />\n但真係柒過籃波好多</blockquote><br />\n各花入各花眼啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似你覺得angelababy美若天仙咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17fff27099b4cebb97c3d1beb2064e7089be37c","tid":374722,"uid":131484,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實香港手球同合球隊，一直係亞洲都好似有唔錯ga成績，只係少人注視。</blockquote><br />\n但真係柒過籃波好多</blockquote><br />\n我反而覺得合球少身體碰撞，適合唔同人一齊挽。同埋我無記錯的話，合球在有防守者係前面時，唔可以射波，更加需要團體合作"},{"pid":"4ba22a6b5fb277e98161d5d0d793a79b7994fe60","tid":374722,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實香港手球同合球隊，一直係亞洲都好似有唔錯ga成績，只係少人注視。</blockquote><br />\n但真係柒過籃波好多</blockquote><br />\n各花入各花眼啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似你覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">angelababy美若天仙</span>咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣嘢係真理，毋容置疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37acce6d0cae27543f6725c9d76122ce1e832778","tid":374722,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實香港手球同合球隊，一直係亞洲都好似有唔錯ga成績，只係少人注視。</blockquote><br />\n但真係柒過籃波好多</blockquote><br />\n我反而覺得合球少身體碰撞，適合唔同人一齊挽。同埋我無記錯的話，合球在有防守者係前面時，唔可以射波，更加需要團體合作</blockquote><br />\n挽你老母"},{"pid":"4b46214775d20a7081376b0b917841494cfab2a0","tid":374722,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實香港手球同合球隊，一直係亞洲都好似有唔錯ga成績，只係少人注視。</blockquote><br />\n但真係柒過籃波好多</blockquote><br />\n我反而覺得合球少身體碰撞，適合唔同人一齊挽。同埋我無記錯的話，合球在有防守者係前面時，唔可以射波，更加需要團體合作</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/lovekorfball/4bbd8d43a54bb.gif?v=1270713672\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Flovekorfball%2F4bbd8d43a54bb.gif%3Fv%3D1270713672&h=9bf45c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到庶民射球唔小心笑咗"},{"pid":"f8ab590a360fcab65f2b5a0cc492b301c4e66817","tid":374722,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實香港手球同合球隊，一直係亞洲都好似有唔錯ga成績，只係少人注視。</blockquote><br />\n但真係柒過籃波好多</blockquote><br />\n各花入各花眼啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似你覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">angelababy美若天仙</span>咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣嘢係真理，毋容置疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把人覺得柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class